# Frontend App Rules

This is part of a pnpm monorepo. See main project rules at `.cursor/rules/crm-rules.mdc`

## shadcn/ui Components

Components are located in the shared `packages/ui` package:

```bash
# From packages/ui directory
cd packages/ui
pnpx shadcn@latest add button

# Or from project root
pnpx shadcn@latest add button --cwd packages/ui
```

## Usage

Import components from the shared UI package:

```tsx
import { Button } from "@crm/ui";
import { Card } from "@crm/ui/components/ui/card";
```

